Package edu.cnm.deepdive.gravity.model

Class Ship

java.lang.Object
edu.cnm.deepdive.gravity.model.Ship
public class Ship extends Object
Represents the player's ship within the game. Manages ship movement, shooting, and interaction with game elements.
